short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Navigate from and to various mapping websites using WebGeo as hub to navigate from one to another.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: webgeo extension is an extension to navigate from and to various mapping websites (google maps, openstreetmap, bing maps, geoportail, nullschool, blitzortung, windy, webgeo) using WebGeo ( https://webgiss.github.io/webgeo/ ) as hub to navigate from one to another.
